<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "ADUAP70A4106021" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Werkingscontrole van rembekrachtiger
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Zorg ervoor dat er geen lucht in de hydraulische leiding zit alsvorens deze controle uit te voeren.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<servinfosub id = "ADUAP70A4106021001">
<title>
Controle op luchtdichtheid
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start de motor.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Zet de motor af nadat hij 1 tot 2 minuten gedraaid heeft.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Druk het rempedaal enkele malen met dezelfde remkracht in als bij normaal remmen en kijk naar de pedaalweg. De rembekrachtiger is luchtdicht als de pedaalweg bij het indrukken telkens korter wordt.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.619mm" ver = "01" gw = "131" gh = "126"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.501in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.579in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.631in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ste
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
2de
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
3de
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Als de pedaalweg niet verandert, is de luchtdichtheid van de rembekrachtiger defect.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Als er een defect wordt vastgesteld, controleer dan de vacuümleidingen en de afdichtende onderdelen en vervang defecte onderdelen. Herhaal daarna de volledige test.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.196mm" ver = "01" gw = "132" gh = "125"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.030in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
1ste, 2de, 3de maal
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "ADUAP70A4106021002">
<title>
Controle van de werking
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Druk bij uitgeschakelde motor het rempedaal enkele malen met dezelfde kracht in en controleer of de pedaalweg niet verandert.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.323mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start de motor terwijl het rempedaal is ingedrukt. Als de pedaalweg van de rembekrachtiger een weinig toeneemt, is de werking in orde. Geen verandering in de pedaalweg wijst op een storing in de rembekrachtiger.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410008.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.958mm" ver = "01" gw = "173" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "ADUAP70A4106021003">
<title>
Controle op luchtdichtheid in beladen toestand
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Druk het rempedaal in terwijl de motor draait. Schakel vervolgens de motor uit terwijl het rempedaal ingedrukt wordt gehouden.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.805mm" ver = "01" gw = "123" gh = "130"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.232in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.628in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Houd ingedrukt
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Houd het rempedaal gedurende 30 seconden ingedrukt. Als de pedaalhoogte niet verandert, is de rembekrachtiger in orde. Als de pedaalhoogte verandert, is de rembekrachtiger niet in goede staat.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01410010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.059mm" ver = "01" gw = "192" gh = "131"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.643in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.382in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.800in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
H: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Houd ingedrukt
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
T: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
30 seconden
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
